          margin: 15px;
          border-radius: 32px;
          box-shadow: 1px 1px 10px 1px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.608);
          font-weight: 700;
          font-family: sans-serif;
          letter-spacing: 2px;
          font-size: 1.3vw;
        "
